{"tid":1711062,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［國際戰線］揾中大港大歷任校長同校友發聲","createTime":"2019-11-12T09:48:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-12T09:52:16.000Z","uid":72962,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"e5a8203b7878abfa2345748339dc8bec5ec55836","tid":1711062,"uid":72962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T09:48:28.000Z","msg":"中大揾沈祖堯同高錕基金會<br />\n<br />\n港大揾馬斐森<br />\n<br />\n仲有佢哋嘅出名嘅校友<br />\n尤其係外國人<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Category:香港中文大學校友\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.m.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FCategory%3A%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E4%B8%AD%E6%96%87%E5%A4%A7%E5%AD%B8%E6%A0%A1%E5%8F%8B&d=9CaroZtPfqcCLVRp0XVEkYWZOtE43EI%2FqUWggxD1P9E%3D&h=3896b5d7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Category:香港中文大學校友</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/香港大學校友列表\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.m.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E5%A4%A7%E5%AD%B8%E6%A0%A1%E5%8F%8B%E5%88%97%E8%A1%A8&d=9CaroZtPfqcCLVRp0XVEkYWZOtE43EI%2FqUWggxD1P9E%3D&h=45dadd35\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/香港大學校友列表</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n中大歷任校長<br />\n<br />\n第1任（1963－1978）：李卓敏教授，經濟學家。<br />\n第2任（1978－1987）：馬臨教授，生物化學家。<br />\n第3任（1987－1996）：高錕教授，光通訊工程學專家。<br />\n第4任（1996－2002）：李國章教授，醫學家。<br />\n第5任（2002－2004）：金耀基教授，社會學家。<br />\n第6任（2004－2010）：劉遵義教授，經濟學家。<br />\n第7任（2010－2017）：沈祖堯教授，醫學家。<br />\n第8任（2018-至今）：段崇智教授，生物醫學家。<br />\n<br />\n港大歷任校長<br />\n<br />\n1965 - 1972\t樂品淳博士（Dr. Kenneth E. Robinson）<br />\n1972 - 1986\t黃麗松教授（Prof. Rayson Huang）<br />\n1986 - 1995\t王賡武教授（Prof. Gungwu Wang）<br />\n1996 - 2000\t鄭耀宗教授（Prof. Yiu-chung Cheng）<br />\n2000 - 2002\t戴義安教授（Prof. William Ian Rees Davies）<br />\n2002 - 2014\t徐立之教授（Prof. Lap-chee Tsui）<br />\n2014 - 2018\t馬斐森教授（Prof. Peter W. Mathieson）<br />\n2018 -\t張翔教授（Prof. Xiang Zhang）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n求下大家一齊幫手揾contact<br />\nSend 畀佢地知<br />\n我自己一個做唔曬"},{"pid":"a0df3e95443d8a20d856bb2bace9426913dfffb8","tid":1711062,"uid":72962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T09:49:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1cf1570af1ca88934fcfed1fd19d3aa06a18fded","tid":1711062,"uid":72962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T09:50:55.000Z","msg":"大學就係connect 上流社會嘅地方<br />\n無人會想見到自己母校畀人搞"},{"pid":"9926fccc9cb27ab15f7009a7138686bdeafbf9bc","tid":1711062,"uid":67212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T09:52:08.000Z","msg":"樓主唔知暴大歷任校長有幾垃圾？佢地唔助攻政府已經好好啦"},{"pid":"eed875bc13ce074e79f5527d1862da993fdac660","tid":1711062,"uid":200971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T09:52:16.000Z","msg":"第4任（1996－2002）：<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">李國章</span></strong></span>教授，醫學家。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}